PRODUCTS; PRODUCT SAFETY; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- LABOR RELATIONS; DEPARTMENT OF 
DEFENSE (U.S.) -- CONTRACTS; WRONGFUL JOB TERMINATION SUITS; MILITARY 
AIRPLANES; AIR FORCE (U.S.); C 5B (AIRPLANE) 
</P>
