rides on his shoulders. ; Photo, Capt. Vince Cocca peers from the window of the 
Hercules C-130. BOB CAREY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Below, Sgt. Robert Bonino 
fastens his safety belt before plane takes off. ; Photo, Darryl Hiton hugs his 
6-month-old son, James, before leaving. BOB CAREY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
