<DOCNO> LA111690-0120 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 308961 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 16, 1990, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2; Column 4; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
580 words 
