GUARD; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- 
FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SAUDI ARABIA; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SAUDI 
ARABIA; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA 
</P>
