the U.S.: "I can't believe how nice we have been treated. It is wonderful." ; 
Photo, Snoopy rubs noses with Mexican guest Eduardo Renteria Ruiz at Knott's. 
GAIL FISHER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
