<P>
MAIL FRAUD; SECURITIES FRAUD; STERNS, DAVID; PYRAMID SCHEMES; ULTIMATE BUSINESS 
NETWORK (COMPANY); NEW SOURCE LTD; WEIGHT REDUCTION; MEDICAL EQUIPMENT AND 
SUPPLIES 
</P>
