that parents on the next fields stop watching their kids and turn around to 
watch the girls." ; Photo, COLOR, Vic Soltan videotapes his granddaughter in 
Puppies-Kittens game. ; Photo, Members of the Cubs and Fledglings make a mad 
dash for the ball during a recent game in Mission Viejo. CHRISTINE COTTER / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
